</span>36-ter; 36-quater,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>commi 5 e 6;
36-quinquies, comma 2; 38; 41; 43, commi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>3,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>4, lettere a), b), d) e g) e
