72-octies,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>commi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1, 2 e 3, 72-decies, commi 1, 2, 3, e 5;<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>66, commi 1 e 4; 67, comma 3; 70, comma 1;
76, commi 1, 2 e 3; 77, comma 4; 84, comma 2; 85, commi 1 e 4; 87, commi 1 e 2;
b-bis)<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>con l'arresto fino a tre mesi o
con l'ammenda da<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>euro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>258<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>euro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1.032<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>la<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>violazione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>degli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>articoli 36-bis,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>commi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>1,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>2, 3, 4, 7; 36-ter; 36-quater,
commi 1, 3, 4; 36-quinquies, comma 1.». <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>- Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>testo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dell'art.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>1, primo comma, del decreto del Presidente<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>della</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Repubblica 7 gennaio 1956, n. 164 (Norme
per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>prevenzione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>degli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>infortuni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sul<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>nelle costruzioni),<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>come<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>modificato dal presente decreto, e' il seguente: <br>
«Art.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>(Attività).<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>- La prevenzione
degli infortuni sul<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>nelle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>costruzioni e' regolata dalle norme del presente<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>gli argomenti non espressamente disciplinati,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>quelle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del decreto del Presidente
della Repubblica<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>27 aprile<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>1955,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>n.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>547,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span><span class=GramE>nonché</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dalle disposizioni<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del decreto legislativo 19 settembre 1994, n.
626, e successive modificazioni.». </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 2</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Al<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>titolo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>decreto legislativo dopo le parole: «99/38/<span class=GramE>CE</span>»
sono aggiunte le seguenti: «2001/45/CE».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>__________________________________<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Nota all'art. 2:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>- Il testo del titolo del citato
decreto legislativo n.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>626<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>1994, come modificato dal presente decreto, e' il<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>seguente: <span class=GramE>«Attuazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>delle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>direttive<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>89/391/CEE,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>89/654/CEE, 89/655/CEE, 89/656/CEE,
90/269/CEE, 90/270/CEE, 90/394/CEE,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>90/679/CEE,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>93/88/CEE,</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>95/63/CE,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>97/42,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>98/24,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>99/38 e 2001/45/CE<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>riguardanti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>il miglioramento della sicurezza e della salute dei lavoratori durante
il lavoro». </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 3</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il presente decreto determina i requisiti
minimi di sicurezza e salute<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>l'uso<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>delle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>attrezzature di lavoro per
l'esecuzione <span class=GramE>di</span> lavori temporanei in quota.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 4</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>All' articolo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>34,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>comma<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>decreto legislativo, dopo la lettera c) <span
class=GramE>viene</span> aggiunta la seguente: «c-bis)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>quota:<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>attività<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavorativa<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che espone il
lavoratore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>al<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>rischio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>caduta<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>una<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>quota<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>posta ad altezza superiore a 2 m rispetto ad un piano stabile».</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> <o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>______________________________________<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Nota all'art. 4:<br>
- Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>testo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dell'art.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>34, comma 1, del citato decreto legislativo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>n.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>626
del 1994, come modificato dal presente decreto, e' il seguente:<br>
«Art</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>34<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>(Definizioni).</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:36.0pt;
margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo2;
tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><![if !supportLists]><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-list:Ignore'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Agli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>effetti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>delle disposizioni di cui al presente titolo <span class=GramE>si </span>intendono
per:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:18.0pt;
margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
font-family:Arial'>a) attrezzatura<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>lavoro:<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>qualsiasi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>macchina, apparecchio, utensile od impianto destinato ad essere
usato&nbsp; durante il lavoro;<br>
b) uso<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>una<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span>attrezzatura<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoro:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>qualsiasi operazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavorativa<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>connessa<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ad<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>una<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>attrezzatura<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di lavoro,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>quale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>messa<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>servizio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>o<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fuori servizio, l'impiego, il trasporto, la
riparazione, la trasformazione,&nbsp; la manutenzione, la pulizia, lo
smontaggio;<br>
c) zona pericolosa: qualsiasi zona all'interno ovvero in prossimità di una
attrezzatura di lavoro nella quale la presenza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoratore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>costituisce un rischio per la salute o la sicurezza dello stesso;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:18.0pt;
margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span class=GramE><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>c-bis</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>)<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>quota:<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>attività<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavorativa che
espone<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>il<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoratore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>al<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>rischio<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di caduta da una quota posta<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ad<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>altezza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>superiore<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>2<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>m rispetto ad un piano
stabile.».</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 5</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:2.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Dopo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>l'articolo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>36<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>decreto legislativo, sono aggiunti i seguenti:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:2.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>36-bis<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>(Obblighi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>del<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>datore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>nell'uso<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span><span class=GramE>di<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>attrezzature
per lavori in quota).&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:2.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 1. Il datore di lavoro, nei casi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>cui<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavori temporanei in quota non possono essere
eseguiti in</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>condizioni<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sicurezza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>condizioni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ergonomiche<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>adeguate a</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>partire<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>luogo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>adatto allo scopo, sceglie
le attrezzature di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoro più idonee a
garantire e mantenere condizioni di lavoro</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>sicure, in conformità ai seguenti criteri:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin-top:2.25pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.25pt;margin-left:
0cm;text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<span class=GramE>a)<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>priorità<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>alle misure di protezione collettiva rispetto
alle<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>misure di protezione
individuale;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) dimensioni
delle attrezzature di lavoro confacenti alla natura dei&nbsp; lavori&nbsp;
da&nbsp; eseguire<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp; alle&nbsp; sollecitazioni
prevedibili e ad una circolazione priva di rischi.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 2.&nbsp;
Il&nbsp; datore&nbsp; di lavoro sceglie il tipo più idoneo di sistema <span
class=GramE>di </span>accesso&nbsp; ai&nbsp; posti&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp;
temporanei&nbsp; in quota in rapporto alla frequenza&nbsp; di circolazione, al
dislivello e alla durata dell'impiego. <span class=GramE>l</span>&nbsp; sistema
di accesso adottato deve consentire l'evacuazione in caso di&nbsp;
pericolo&nbsp; imminente.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; passaggio&nbsp; da&nbsp; un&nbsp;
sistema di accesso a piattaforme,&nbsp; impalcati,&nbsp; passerelle&nbsp; e
viceversa non deve comportare rischi ulteriori di caduta.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 3. Il datore
di lavoro dispone affinché sia utilizzata una scala a pioli&nbsp; quale&nbsp;
posto&nbsp; di lavoro in quota solo nei casi in cui l'uso <span class=GramE>di </span>altre&nbsp;&nbsp;
attrezzature&nbsp;&nbsp; di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; considerate&nbsp; più&nbsp;
sicure&nbsp; non&nbsp; e' giustificato&nbsp; a&nbsp; causa&nbsp; del limitato
livello di rischio e della breve durata di impiego oppure delle caratteristiche
esistenti dei siti che non può modificare.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 4. Il datore
di lavoro dispone affinché siano impiegati sistemi <span class=GramE>di </span>accesso
e di posizionamento mediante funi alle quali il lavoratore e'
direttamente&nbsp; sostenuto,&nbsp; soltanto&nbsp; in&nbsp; circostanze in cui,
a seguito della&nbsp; valutazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp; rischi,&nbsp; risulta&nbsp;
che&nbsp; il lavoro può essere effettuato&nbsp; in&nbsp; condizioni&nbsp;
di&nbsp; sicurezza&nbsp; e&nbsp; l'impiego&nbsp; di&nbsp; un'altra
attrezzatura&nbsp; di lavoro considerata più sicura non e' giustificato a causa
della breve durata di impiego e delle caratteristiche esistenti dei&nbsp; siti
che non può modificare. Lo stesso datore di lavoro prevede l'impiego&nbsp;
di&nbsp; un&nbsp; sedile&nbsp; munito&nbsp; di&nbsp; <span class=GramE>appositi</span>
accessori in funzione dell'esito&nbsp; della&nbsp; valutazione&nbsp; dei&nbsp;
rischi ed, in particolare, della durata dei lavori e dei vincoli di carattere
ergonomico.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 5.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>datore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro, <span class=GramE>in relazione al</span>
tipo di attrezzature di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavoro adottate in
base ai commi precedenti, individua le misure atte</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a minimizzare i rischi per i lavoratori,
insiti nelle attrezzature in</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>questione,
prevedendo, ove necessario, l'installazione di dispositivi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>protezione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>contro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>cadute.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>I<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>predetti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dispositivi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>devono</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>presentare<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>una configurazione ed una resistenza tali da evitare o da</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>arrestare<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>le cadute da luoghi di lavoro in quota e da prevenire, <span
class=GramE>per<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>quanto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>possibile, eventuali lesioni</span> dei
lavoratori. I dispositivi di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>protezione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>collettiva<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>contro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>cadute<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>possono<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>presentare</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>interruzioni<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>soltanto nei punti in cui sono presenti scale
a pioli o</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a gradini.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 6. Il datore
di lavoro nel caso in cui l'esecuzione di un lavoro di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>natura<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>particolare<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>richiede<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>l'eliminazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>temporanea<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dispositivo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di protezione collettiva contro le cadute, adotta misure</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sicurezza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>equivalenti<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ed efficaci. Il lavoro e' eseguito previa</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>adozione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>tali<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>misure.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span><span class=GramE>Una<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>volta<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>terminato</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>definitivamente o</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>temporaneamente<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>detto lavoro di natura particolare, i
dispositivi di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>protezione
collettiva contro le cadute devono essere ripristinati.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:
Arial'>7.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>datore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>effettua</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavori temporanei in quota</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>soltanto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>se<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le
condizioni meteorologiche non mettono in pericolo la</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>sicurezza
e la salute dei lavoratori.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Art.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>36-ter<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>(Obblighi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>datore di lavoro <span class=GramE>relativi all'</span>impiego</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>delle<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scale a pioli).&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 1. Il datore
di lavoro assicura che le scale</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>siano<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sistemate<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>modo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da garantire la loro
stabilità</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>durante l'impiego e
secondo i seguenti criteri:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
a)<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>portatili devono poggiare su un supporto</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>stabile,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>resistente,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dimensioni adeguate e immobile, in modo da</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>garantire la posizione orizzontale dei
pioli;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>b) le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sospese<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>devono essere agganciate in modo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>sicuro e, ad eccezione delle scale a funi, in maniera tale
da evitare</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>spostamenti e
qualsiasi movimento <span class=GramE>di </span>oscillazione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>c) lo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scivolamento<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>piede<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>delle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a pioli portatili,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>durante<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>loro uso, deve essere impedito
con fissaggio della parte</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>superiore<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>o<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>inferiore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>montanti,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>o<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>con qualsiasi dispositivo</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>antiscivolo,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>o<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>ricorrendo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a qualsiasi altra
soluzione <span class=GramE>di </span>efficacia</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>equivalente;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>d) le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>usate per l'accesso devono essere tali da</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sporgere<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a sufficienza oltre il livello <span class=GramE>di </span>accesso, a
meno che altri</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>dispositivi
garantiscono una presa sicura;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e) le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>composte <span class=GramE>da</span> più elementi
innestabili o a</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sfilo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>devono<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>essere<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>utilizzate<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>modo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>assicurare<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>il fermo</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>reciproco dei vari
elementi;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>f) le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pioli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>mobili<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>devono essere fissate stabilmente</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>prima di <span class=GramE>accedervi</span>.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 2.&nbsp; Il&nbsp; datore&nbsp;
di&nbsp; lavoro&nbsp; assicura&nbsp; che&nbsp; le&nbsp; scale&nbsp; a pioli
siano utilizzate&nbsp; in&nbsp; modo&nbsp; da&nbsp; consentire&nbsp; ai&nbsp;
lavoratori&nbsp; di&nbsp; disporre in qualsiasi&nbsp;&nbsp; momento&nbsp;
di&nbsp; un&nbsp; appoggio&nbsp; e&nbsp; di&nbsp; una&nbsp; presa&nbsp;
sicuri.&nbsp; In particolare il trasporto a mano di pesi su una scala a pioli
non deve precludere una presa sicura.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>«Art.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>36-quater (Obblighi del datore di lavoro <span
class=GramE>relativi all'</span>impiego</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>dei<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ponteggi).&nbsp;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 1. Il datore
di lavoro procede alla redazione di un</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>calcolo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>resistenza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>stabilità<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>delle<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>corrispondenti</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>configurazioni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span><span
class=GramE>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span>impiego,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>se <span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>nella<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>relazione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>calcolo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>del</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ponteggio<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>scelto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>non<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sono<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>disponibili<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>specifiche<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>configurazioni</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>strutturali con i relativi schemi di
impiego.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>2. Il datore di lavoro e' esonerato
dall'obbligo di cui al comma 1,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>se
provvede all'assemblaggio del ponteggio in conformità ai capi IV,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>V e VI del decreto del Presidente <span
class=GramE>della</span> Repubblica 7 gennaio 1956, n. 164.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>3.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>datore<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>provvede<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a</span> redigere a mezzo di persona</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>competente un piano di montaggio, uso e
smontaggio, in funzione della</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>complessità<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del ponteggio scelto. Tale piano può assumere
la forma</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>piano <span class=GramE>di </span>applicazione generalizzata integrato
da istruzioni e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>progetti<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>particolareggiati<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>gli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>schemi speciali costituenti
il</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ponteggio,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ed<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e'<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>messo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>a<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>disposizione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del preposto addetto
alla</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sorveglianza e dei
lavoratori interessati.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>4. Il datore di lavoro assicura che:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lo scivolamento degli elementi <span
class=GramE>di </span>appoggio di un ponteggio e'</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>impedito<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>tramite<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fissaggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>su una superficie di appoggio, o con un</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>dispositivo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>antiscivolo,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>oppure<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>con<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>qualsiasi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>altra soluzione di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>efficacia equivalente;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>b) i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>piani<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>posa dei predetti elementi <span class=GramE>di
</span>appoggio hanno una</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>
</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>capacità
portante sufficiente;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>c) il ponteggio e' stabile;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>d) dispositivi appropriati impediscono lo
spostamento</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>involontario dei
ponteggi su ruote durante l'esecuzione dei lavori in</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>quota;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>) le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dimensioni,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>la forma e la disposizione degli impalcati di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>un ponteggio sono idonee alla natura del
lavoro da eseguire, adeguate</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ai<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>carichi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>da<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sopportare<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>tali<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>da consentire un'esecuzione
dei</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lavori e una
circolazione sicure;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>f) il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>montaggio degli impalcati dei ponteggi e' tale da impedire</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>lo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>spostamento<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>degli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>elementi <span class=GramE>componenti</span>
durante l'uso, nonché la</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>presenza di spazi
vuoti pericolosi fra gli elementi che costituiscono</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>gli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>impalcati<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dispositivi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>verticali di
protezione collettiva</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>contro le cadute.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>5.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>datore<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>provvede<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ad<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>evidenziare</span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>parti di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>ponteggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>non pronte
per l'uso, in particolare durante le operazioni</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>montaggio,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>smontaggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>o trasformazione, mediante segnaletica di</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>avvertimento<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>pericolo<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>generico ai sensi del decreto legislativo</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>14 agosto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>1996,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>n.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>493, e delimitandole con elementi materiali che</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>impediscono l'accesso alla zona di
pericolo.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>6.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>datore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>assicura<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che i ponteggi siano
montati,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>smontati<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>o<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>trasformati<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sotto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sorveglianza di un preposto e <span class=GramE>ad<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>opera</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoratori<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>hanno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>ricevuto una formazione adeguata e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>mirata alle operazioni previste.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>7.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>La<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formazione <span class=GramE>di
cui al comma 6</span> ha carattere teorico-pratico e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>deve riguardare:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>a)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>comprensione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>piano<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>montaggio,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>smontaggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>o<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>trasformazione del
ponteggio;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>b) la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sicurezza durante le operazioni di montaggio, smontaggio o</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>trasformazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>del<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>ponteggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>con<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>riferimento<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>alla<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>legislazione</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>vigente; </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>c) le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>misure di prevenzione dei rischi di caduta di persone o <span
class=GramE>di<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span></span>oggetti;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>d) le misure di sicurezza
in caso di cambiamento delle condizioni<span style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'>
</span>meteorologiche pregiudizievoli alla sicurezza del ponteggio;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>e</span>) le condizioni
di carico ammissibile; </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>f) qualsiasi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>altro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>rischio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>suddette<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>operazioni<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>montaggio, smontaggio o trasformazione possono comportare.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp; </span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>8.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>In<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sede<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Conferenza Stato-Regioni e <span class=GramE>province autonome sono<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>individuati</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>soggetti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formatori,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>durata,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>gli indirizzi ed i</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>requisiti minimi di validità dei corsi.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>9.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>I<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoratori<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>alla data <span class=GramE>di </span>entrata in vigore del presente</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>hanno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>svolto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>almeno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>due<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>anni attività di montaggio</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>smontaggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>o trasformazione di ponteggi sono tenuti a partecipare ai</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>corsi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>cui
al comma 8 entro i due anni successivi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>alla data di entrata in vigore del presente decreto.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'> </span>10.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>I<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>preposti che alla data <span
class=GramE>di </span>entrata in vigore del presente</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>hanno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>svolto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>almeno tre anni operazioni di montaggio,</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>smontaggio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>o
trasformazione di ponteggi sono tenuti a partecipare ai</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>corsi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formazione<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>cui
al comma 8 entro i due anni successivi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>alla data di entrata in vigore del presente decreto.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>«Art.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>36-quinquies<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>(Obblighi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>datori<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>concernenti</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>l'impiego<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sistemi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span><span class=GramE>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span>accesso<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>posizionamento<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>mediante</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>funi).</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp; 1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>datore<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>impiega<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sistemi <span
class=GramE>di </span>accesso e di</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>posizionamento mediante funi in conformità ai seguenti
requisiti:</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>a)<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sistema<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>comprendente almeno due funi ancorate separatamente,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>una<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>l'accesso,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>discesa<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sostegno (fune di lavoro) e</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>l'al</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%;font-family:Arial'>tra<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>con<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>funzione di dispositivo ausiliario (fune di
sicurezza).</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>E'<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ammesso l'uso di una fune in circostanze
eccezionali in cui l'uso</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>una<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>seconda<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fune<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>rende<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>più<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>pericoloso e se sono</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>adottate
misure adeguate per garantire la sicurezza;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>b) lavoratori<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dotati<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un'adeguata<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>imbracatura<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>sostegno<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>collegata alla fune di sicurezza;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>c) fune di lavoro
munita di meccanismi sicuri <span class=GramE>di </span>ascesa e discesa</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dotata<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>un sistema autobloccante volto a evitare la
caduta nel</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>caso<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>in<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>cui
l'utilizzatore perda il controllo dei propri movimenti.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>La<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fune<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sicurezza<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>deve<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>essere munita di un dispositivo mobile</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>contro le cadute che <span class=GramE>segue</span>
gli spostamenti del lavoratore;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>d) attrezzi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>ed<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>altri<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>accessori<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>utilizzati<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dai<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoratori,</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>agganciati<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>alla<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>loro imbracatura di sostegno
o al sedile o ad altro</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>strumento idoneo;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
class=GramE><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>e)
lavori<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>programmati<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sorvegliati in modo adeguato, anche al</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>fine<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>poter<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>immediatamente<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>soccorrere<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>il lavoratore in caso di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>nece</span></span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ssità.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Il programma dei lavori definisce un piano <span
class=GramE>di </span>emergenza,</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>le<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>tipologie<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>operative, i dispositivi di protezione individuale, le</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>tecniche<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>le procedure operative, gli
ancoraggi, il posizionamento</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>degli<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>operatori,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>metodi<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>accesso, le squadre di lavoro e gli</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>attrezzi di lavoro;</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>f) il programma di lavoro deve essere disponibile
presso i luoghi</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>ai<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fini della verifica da parte <span
class=GramE>dell'</span>organo di vigilanza</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>competente<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>territorio<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>compatibilità<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ai<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>criteri<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>cui</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;
font-family:Arial'>all'articolo 36-bis, commi 1 e 2.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>2.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Il<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>datore<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoro<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fornisce<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ai lavoratori interessati una formazione
adeguata e mirata alle operazioni previste, in particolare</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>in materia di procedure di salvataggio.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>3.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>La<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formazione <span class=GramE>di
cui al comma 2</span> ha carattere teorico-pratico e</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>deve riguardare:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>a) l'apprendimento<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>delle<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>tecniche<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>operative<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dell'uso<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>dispositivi necessari;</span></span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>b) l'addestramento<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>specifico<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sia<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>su strutture naturali, sia su</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>manufatti;</span><span style='font-size:
8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>c) l'utilizzo<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dispositivi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>protezione individuale, loro<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>caratteristiche tecniche,
manutenzione, durata e conservazione;</span></span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>d) gli elementi di primo soccorso;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span><span class=GramE>e</span>) i rischi
oggettivi e le misure di prevenzione e protezione;</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>    </span>f) le procedure di salvataggio.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>4.<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>In
sede di Conferenza Stato-Regioni e <span class=GramE>province autonome saranno<span
style='font-family:"Times New Roman"'> </span>individuati</span><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>i<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>soggetti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>formatori,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>la<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>durata,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>gli indirizzi ed i</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>requisiti minimi di validità dei corsi.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>5. I<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>lavoratori<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>alla<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>data <span class=GramE>di </span>entrata in vigore del presente</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>decreto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>hanno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>svolto<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>per<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>almeno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>2<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>anni attività con impiego di</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>sistemi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>di accesso e posizionamento mediante funi devono partecipare</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>ai<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>corsi di formazione di cui al comma 4 entro i due anni successivi</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'> </span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;
line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>alla data di entrata in vigore del presente
decreto».<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 6</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>In relazione a</span>
quanto disposto dall'articolo 117, quinto comma, della<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Costituzione le norme del presente decreto
afferenti a materie di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>competenza
legislativa delle regioni e delle province autonome di Trento<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>Bolzano,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>che non abbiano ancora
provveduto al recepimento della<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>direttiva<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>2001/45 del Parlamento
europeo e del Consiglio, del 27 giugno<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>2001,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>si<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>applicano<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>sino<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>alla data di entrata in
vigore della<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>normativa<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>attuazione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>di<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ciascuna<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>regione<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>provincia autonoma,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>   </span>nel<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  
</span>rispetto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>vincoli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>derivanti<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dall'ordinamento
comunitario<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>e<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>dei<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>principi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fondamentali<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>desumibili<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>dal presente decreto.</span><span style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:
120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>

<hr size=1 width=300 style='width:225.0pt' align=center>

</span></div>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Note all'art. 6:</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>- Il&nbsp;&nbsp; testo&nbsp;&nbsp;
dell'art.&nbsp;&nbsp; 117<span class=GramE>,</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;
quinto&nbsp;&nbsp; comma&nbsp; della Costituzione, e' il seguente:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>«Le&nbsp; regioni&nbsp; e&nbsp;
le&nbsp; province&nbsp; autonome&nbsp; di Trento e di Bolzano, nelle materie di
loro competenza, partecipano alle decisioni&nbsp; dirette&nbsp; alla&nbsp;
formazione&nbsp; degli&nbsp; atti normativi comunitari&nbsp; e&nbsp;
provvedono&nbsp; all'attuazione&nbsp; e all'esecuzione degli&nbsp;
accordi&nbsp; internazionali&nbsp; e&nbsp; degli&nbsp; atti&nbsp; dell'Unione
europea, nel rispetto delle norme di procedura stabilite da legge dello Stato,
che disciplina le <span class=GramE>modalità</span> di esercizio del potere
sostitutivo in caso di inadempienza.».<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>- Per&nbsp; i&nbsp; riferimenti della
citata direttiva 2001/45 si veda la nota al titolo.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<pre style='text-align:justify'><span style='font-size:8.0pt'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></pre>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>Art. 7</span></b><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;font-family:Arial'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>1.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Le<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>disposizioni<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>del<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>presente decreto entrano in vigore il 19
luglio 2005. Il presente decreto, munito del sigillo dello Stato, sarà inserito
nella<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Raccolta<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>ufficiale<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>degli<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>atti<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>normativi<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>della<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>Repubblica italiana.<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span><span class=GramE>E'<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>fatto<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'> 
</span>obbligo a chiunque spetti</span> di osservarlo e farlo osservare.</span><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:120%'><span
style='font-size:8.0pt;line-height:120%;font-family:Arial'>Dato a Roma, addì&nbsp;
8 luglio 2003<o:p></o:p></span></p>

